<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.10">
<l>kaṉṉiyarō ṭeṅkaḷ nampi kariya pirāṉviḷai yāṭṭaip</l>
<l>poṉṉiyal māṭaṅkaḷ cūḻnta putuvaiyar kōṉpaṭṭaṉ kōtai</l>
<l>iṉṉicai yāṟcoṉṉa mālai yīraintum vallavar tāmpōy</l>
<l>maṉṉiya mātava ṉōṭu vaikuntam pukkirup pārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those 	capable [of mastering] the garland of ten [songs] that</l>
<l rend="indent">Kōtai, [daughter of] Bhaṭṭa, the king of the people of Putuvai with mansions</l>
<l rend="indent">made of gold,</l>
<l rend="indent">composed with sweet music</l>
<l rend="indent">[describing] the games of our perfect man, the dark Lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">with the [cowherd] maidens,</l>
<l>will go to, enter, and remain in Vaikuṇṭha along with Mādhava,</l>
<l rend="indent">who [resides there] permanently.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
